  <itemBody>
    <div class="grid-row">
      <div class="col-12">
        <p id="stimulus">
            During more than 30 years, the American Space Shuttle transported 355 astronauts in space over 135
            orbital launchings from Cap Canaveral, Florida. This 2046-ton Behemoth traveled 870 million kilometers
            around the Earth from 12th of April 1981 to 21st of July 2011. The National Aeronautics and Space
            Administration (NASA) built 5 Space Shuttles: Columbia, Challenger, Discovery, Atlantis and Endeavour.
		</p>
